<footer class="mt-5 pt-4 pb-4 bg-light border-top">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 mb-md-0">
        <h5 class="mb-3"><i class="bi bi-journal-richtext me-2"></i>MDBlog</h5>
        <p class="text-muted">
          MongoDB와 Express.js를 사용한 현대적인 블로그 시스템입니다. 마크다운을
          지원하고 태그와 카테고리로 콘텐츠를 관리할 수 있습니다.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 mb-4 mb-md-0">
        <h5 class="mb-3">바로가기</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="/" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-house-door me-1"></i>홈
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="/posts" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-file-text me-1"></i>최신 게시물
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="/categories" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-folder me-1"></i>카테고리 목록
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/tags" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-tags me-1"></i>태그 목록
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-2 mb-4 mb-md-0">
        <h5 class="mb-3">계정</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <% if (locals.currentUser) { %>
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="/auth/profile" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-person me-1"></i>내 프로필
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="/posts/my-posts" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text me-1"></i>내 게시물
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/auth/logout" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right me-1"></i>로그아웃
            </a>
          </li>
          <% } else { %>
          <li class="mb-2">
            <a href="/auth/login" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-1"></i>로그인
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/auth/register" class="text-decoration-none">
              <i class="bi bi-person-plus me-1"></i>회원가입
            </a>
          </li>
          <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <h5 class="mb-3">소셜 미디어</h5>
        <div class="d-flex gap-3">
          <a
            href="#"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-decoration-none fs-4"
            title="GitHub"
          >
            <i class="bi bi-github"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-decoration-none fs-4"
            title="Twitter"
          >
            <i class="bi bi-twitter"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-decoration-none fs-4"
            title="Facebook"
          >
            <i class="bi bi-facebook"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-decoration-none fs-4"
            title="LinkedIn"
          >
            <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-decoration-none fs-4"
            title="Instagram"
          >
            <i class="bi bi-instagram"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <h6 class="mb-2">뉴스레터 구독</h6>
          <form>
            <div class="input-group">
              <input
                type="email"
                class="form-control"
                placeholder="이메일 주소"
                aria-label="Newsletter email"
              />
              <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">구독</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="my-4" />
    <div
      class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between align-items-center"
    >
      <p class="text-muted mb-3 mb-md-0">
        © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MDBlog. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <div>
        <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-muted me-3"
          >개인정보처리방침</a
        >
        <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-muted">이용약관</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

